
Firewire (IEEE 1394) -- tree identification protocol (tip)

according to special number of Formal Aspects of Computing (volume 14, num 3)
particularly article "Using SPIN to Analyse the Firewire protocol"

parameters:
-T topology
 1 = line with N nodes
 2 = fixed acyclic with 6 nodes
 3 = fixed cyclic with 6 nodes
- velikost bufferu

It is not completely finished... je to proste blbe, protoze nemam kanal mezi
kazdyma dvema, takze si muzu precist zpravu jindy nez kdyz ju chcu....

